dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of 59,642 doctor-patient dialogue records in both English and Chinese, covering topics such as the interpretation of orthodontic images, diagnosis, and treatment recommendations.
dcterms:title: Medical Domain Question-Answering Dataset (MD-QA)

dcterms:description: A multimodal dataset that includes orthodontic medical images and corresponding textual diagnostic reports, covering various types and conditions of orthodontic craniofacial imaging and measurement.
dcterms:title: Orthodontic Craniofacial Imaging and Measurement Multimodal Dataset (OCIMM Dataset)
